{"article_id":"1onOq6jKz1LGEY2H","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Joe Biden released a statement Friday","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"denying a former aide 's claims","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"he sexually assaulted her 27 years ago ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"saying of Tara Reade 's allegation :","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"`` This never happened . ''","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Friday 's statement is the first detailed response from Biden to Reade 's allegation","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"and comes as pressure","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"built on the presumptive Democratic nominee","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"to personally address the matter .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"`` While the details of these allegations of sexual harassment and sexual assault are complicated ,","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"two things are not complicated .","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"One is that women deserve to be treated with dignity and respect ,","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"and","depth":14},{"id":14,"text":"when they step forward","depth":15},{"id":15,"text":"they should be heard ,","depth":16},{"id":16,"text":"not silenced .","depth":16},{"id":17,"text":"The second is that their stories should be subject to appropriate inquiry and scrutiny , ''","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"the former vice president and presumptive Democratic 2020 nominee said in the statement .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"He continued ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"`` Responsible news organizations should examine and evaluate the full and growing record of inconsistencies in her story ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"which has changed repeatedly in both small and big ways . ''","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"`` But this much bears emphasizing , ''","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"`` She has said","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"she raised some of these issues with her supervisor and senior staffers from my office at the time .","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"They","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"-- both men and a woman --","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"have said , unequivocally ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"that she never came to them","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"and complained","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"or raised issues .","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"News organizations","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"that have talked with literally dozens of former staffers","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"have not found one","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"-- not one --","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"who corroborated her allegations in any way .","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"Indeed , many of them spoke to the culture of an office","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"that would not have tolerated harassment in any way","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"-- as indeed I would not have . ''","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"In the MSNBC interview , Biden said","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"he is `` saying unequivocally ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"it never , never happened .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"It did n't .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"It never happened . ''","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"he has not reached out to Reade ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"and does not remember her making any complaint .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"`` This never happened ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"when she first made the claim ,","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"we made it clear","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"that it never happened ,","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"and it 's as simple as that , ''","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Biden 's only response for weeks has been a statement from deputy campaign manager Kate Bedingfield","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"highlighting the former vice president 's role","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"in crafting the Violence Against Women Act","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"and saying","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"what Reade had claimed `` absolutely did not happen . ''","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Former Biden staffers also said","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Reade had not complained about Biden at the time .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"The allegation comes","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"as Biden is preparing to take on President Donald Trump in the general election .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"More than a dozen women have leveled allegations against Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"ranging from unwelcome advances to sexual harassment and assault .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Trump has denied those allegations .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"For some of Biden 's supporters and surrogates , questions","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"related to Reade 's allegation","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"have presented a challenging balancing act","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"-- of expressing support for Biden 's candidacy and character","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"while not dismissing a sexual assault allegation .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Democrats in particular have vocally championed the # MeToo movement in recent years ,","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"advocating","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that all accusers to be fully heard and recognized .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"And gender dynamics are expected to remain at the forefront of the 2020 race ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"as Biden begins his search for a female running mate .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Some of the women","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"widely expected to be on Biden 's shortlist of vice presidential nominees ,","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"including Michigan Gov . Gretchen Whitmer and Minnesota Sen. Amy Klobuchar ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"have recently been asked about the allegation ;","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Biden 's allies have pointed to his decades-long advocacy for women and victims of abuse ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"including his work on the Violence Against Women Act .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Biden said in the MSNBC interview","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"he did not know","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"why Reade was now alleging","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"he had sexually assaulted her .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"`` I 'm not going to question her motive , ''","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"`` I do n't know","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"why she 's saying this .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"I do n't know","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"why after 27 years all of a sudden this gets raised .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"I do n't understand it . ''","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"`` She has a right","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"to say whatever she wants to say .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"But I have a right","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"to say ,","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"look at the facts , ''","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Reade ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"who worked as a junior staffer at Biden 's office in 1993 ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"had publicly accused Biden last year of touching her shoulders and neck","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"and making her feel uncomfortable .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"Reade first came forward with her sexual assault allegation against Biden in interviews this year with multiple media outlets ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"including CNN .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"She told CNN","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"that in 1993 ,","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"when she was working as an aide in Biden 's Senate office ,","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"she was asked to deliver a duffel bag to the then-Delaware senator .","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"In a corridor somewhere in the Capitol Hill complex , Reade said","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"Biden `` had me up against the wall ;","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"he used his knee","depth":16},{"id":113,"text":"to spread open my legs , ''","depth":16},{"id":114,"text":"and `` put his fingers inside me . ''","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"A friend of Reade 's ,","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"who asked to remain anonymous","depth":16},{"id":117,"text":"in order to protect her privacy ,","depth":16},{"id":118,"text":"told CNN","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"that Reade had told her in detail","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"that she had been sexually assaulted by Biden on Capitol Hill .","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"The friend said","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"she believes","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"Reade called her within days of the alleged assault .","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"former neighbor of Reade has come forward","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"and told CNN","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"that Reade told her about the alleged assault within a few years of the incident , in the mid-1990s ,","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"and a newly surfaced video from 1993 appears to feature Reade 's mother","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"calling into `` Larry King Live ''","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"to seek advice around the time of the alleged assault about how to handle `` problems ''","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"her daughter had","depth":15},{"id":131,"text":"while working for a prominent US senator .","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"Reade told CNN","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"that she is certain","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"the voice in the video belongs to her mother , Jeanette Altimus ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"who died a few years ago .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"The Washington Post interviewed Reade 's brother , Collin Moulton ,","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"who told the paper","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"that she had told him in 1993","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"that Biden had `` behaved inappropriately","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"by touching her neck and shoulders ''","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"but not about the alleged sexual assault .","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"Several days after that interview with Reade 's brother , the Post said ,","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"`` he said in a text message","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"that he recalled her telling him","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"that Biden had put his hand 'under her clothes . ' ''","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"Moulton later told CNN in a text message","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"that Reade told him in the early 1990s","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"that she had been asked to bring Biden his gym bag ,","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"and that in a private setting , he had cornered her against the wall","depth":15},{"id":150,"text":"and put his hands under her clothes .","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"Reade has said","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"that she complained to multiple colleagues in the office about interactions with Biden","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"that made her uncomfortable ,","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"but not about the alleged assault .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"Reade has also said","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"that she filed a complaint with a personnel office on Capitol Hill at the time ,","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"but that she does not have a copy of it .","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"It is unclear what kind of complaint","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"-- and at what office --","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"Reade may have filed .","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"Pressure has mounted on Biden to release his papers from his Senate days ,","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"which","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"some say","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"could shed light on the allegation .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"Those papers are at the University of Delaware","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"and will not be made publicly available until two years after Biden leaves public life .","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"The university said this week","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"it is still curating the collection of documents , a process","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"expected to last into the spring of 2021 .","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"Therefore ,","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"a university spokesperson said Thursday ,","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"it can not identify what documents and files can be found in the collection .","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"Biden says","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"his papers at the university do not contain personnel files .","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"But ,","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"personnel files from the Senate during those days would be kept at the National Archives .","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"`` I am requesting","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"that the Secretary of the Senate ask the Archives to identify any record of the complaint","depth":14},{"id":180,"text":"she alleges","depth":15},{"id":181,"text":"she filed","depth":15},{"id":182,"text":"and make available to the press any such document .","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"If there was ever any such complaint ,","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"the record will be there , ''","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"Biden said .","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"Later on Friday afternoon , Biden sent a letter to the secretary of the Senate","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"asking that office to work with the National Archives","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"to locate and release any complaint from Reade as well as `` any and all other documents in the records","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"that relate to the allegation . ''","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"The National Archives said in an email to CNN","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"that any personnel complaints from 1993 would have `` remained under the control of the Senate . ''","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"`` I am writing to request your assistance","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":"in determining","depth":15},{"id":194,"text":"whether 27 years ago a staff member in my United States Senate office filed a complaint","depth":16},{"id":195,"text":"alleging sexual harassment , ''","depth":16},{"id":196,"text":"Biden wrote .","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"`` According to public reports ,","depth":15},{"id":198,"text":"the staff member , Ms. Tara Reade , has stated","depth":15},{"id":199,"text":"that in 1993 she filed such a complaint with the office","depth":15},{"id":200,"text":"responsible for enforcing Senate employees ' rights in the workplace . ''","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"He added ,","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"`` I request","depth":15},{"id":203,"text":"that you take or direct whatever steps are necessary","depth":18},{"id":204,"text":"to establish the location of the records of this Office ,","depth":18},{"id":205,"text":"and","depth":18},{"id":206,"text":"once they have been located ,","depth":20},{"id":207,"text":"to direct a search for the alleged complaint","depth":20},{"id":208,"text":"and to make public the results of this search .","depth":19},{"id":209,"text":"I would ask","depth":17},{"id":210,"text":"that the public release include not only a complaint","depth":19},{"id":211,"text":"if one exists ,","depth":19},{"id":212,"text":"but any and all other documents in the records","depth":19},{"id":213,"text":"that relate to the allegation . ''","depth":19},{"id":214,"text":"Biden also said on MSNBC","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"that the his papers at the University of Delaware will remain sealed","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"because they could become political `` fodder '' during his presidential campaign .","depth":12},{"id":217,"text":"`` The idea","depth":14},{"id":218,"text":"that they would all be made public","depth":15},{"id":219,"text":"while I was running for office","depth":15},{"id":220,"text":"can be taken out of context , ''","depth":13},{"id":221,"text":"Biden said .","depth":12},{"id":222,"text":"He added","depth":11},{"id":223,"text":"that the documents would cover topics like meetings with foreign heads of state .","depth":11},{"id":224,"text":"Asked whether he would release all complaints against him ,","depth":10},{"id":225,"text":"Biden said ,","depth":11},{"id":226,"text":"`` I 'm prepared to do that , ''","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"and that to the best of his knowledge there are no claims of sexual misconduct on his part .","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"CNN has interviewed half a dozen former Biden aides","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"who worked in his Senate office in the early 1990s .","depth":9},{"id":230,"text":"All of them said","depth":9},{"id":231,"text":"they were not aware of any sexual harassment or assault allegations .","depth":9},{"id":232,"text":"Marianne Baker ,","depth":11},{"id":233,"text":"who was Biden 's executive assistant in the 1980s and 1990s","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"when Biden was a senator ,","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"also previously said in a statement","depth":12},{"id":236,"text":"provided through the Biden campaign","depth":12},{"id":237,"text":"that she was never aware of any reports of inappropriate conduct , including from Reade .","depth":11},{"id":238,"text":"`` In all my years","depth":15},{"id":239,"text":"working for Senator Biden ,","depth":15},{"id":240,"text":"I never once witnessed , or heard of , or received , any reports of inappropriate conduct , period","depth":14},{"id":241,"text":"-- not from Ms. Reade , not from anyone .","depth":13},{"id":242,"text":"I have absolutely no knowledge or memory of Ms. Reade 's accounting of events ,","depth":13},{"id":243,"text":"which would have left a searing impression on me as a woman professional , and as a manager , ''","depth":13},{"id":244,"text":"Baker said .","depth":11},{"id":245,"text":"`` These clearly false allegations are in complete contradiction to both the inner workings of our Senate office and to the man","depth":11},{"id":246,"text":"I know","depth":12},{"id":247,"text":"and worked so closely with for almost two decades . ''","depth":12},{"id":248,"text":"Dennis Toner ,","depth":12},{"id":249,"text":"who was Biden 's deputy chief of staff at the time and one of the people","depth":14},{"id":250,"text":"Reade said","depth":14},{"id":251,"text":"she had discussed her complaints with ,","depth":13},{"id":252,"text":"told CNN in an interview on Thursday","depth":11},{"id":253,"text":"that he had no recollection of Reade or any conversation","depth":11},{"id":254,"text":"related to sexual harassment allegations .","depth":11},{"id":255,"text":"`` I clearly would remember","depth":11},{"id":256,"text":"if we --","depth":15},{"id":257,"text":"that is ,","depth":16},{"id":258,"text":"if Tara and myself --","depth":16},{"id":259,"text":"had any kind of conversation","depth":16},{"id":260,"text":"regarding sexual harassment allegations ,","depth":16},{"id":261,"text":"let alone something","depth":16},{"id":262,"text":"involving Sen. Biden .","depth":16},{"id":263,"text":"It would stick in my mind .","depth":14},{"id":264,"text":"It would be burned in my mind , ''","depth":14},{"id":265,"text":"Toner said .","depth":12},{"id":266,"text":"`` I do n't understand it . ''","depth":10},{"id":267,"text":"This story has been updated with additional comments from Biden 's statement and from his interview on MSNBC .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":535,"left":534,"right":267,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":534,"left":0,"right":533,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":533,"left":333,"right":532,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":333,"left":328,"right":332,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":328,"left":321,"right":327,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":321,"left":276,"right":320,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":272,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":270,"right":271,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":1,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":271,"left":4,"right":5,"relation"